name: CISCO ESTREAMER [Intrusion Event Record]
description: This rule looks for intrusion event records of Cisco eStreamer based on the high severity value.

name: CISCO ESTREAMER [Intrusion Event Record]
description: This rule looks for intrusion event records of Cisco eStreamer based on the medium severity value.

name: CISCO ESTREAMER [Intrusion Event Record]
description: This rule looks for intrusion event records of Cisco eStreamer based on the low severity value.

name: CISCO FMC [<%= eventname %>]
description: This rule looks for a high number of Network Intrusion events from same source where action was not blocked.
query: class=cisco_fmc impact=[1,2] NOT action:`blocked` NOT srcipv4:$exclusions.global.srcipv4

name: CISCO FMC [<%= eventname %>]
description: This rule looks for a high number of Network Intrusion events from same source where action was not blocked.
query: class=cisco_fmc impact=[3,4] NOT action:blocked NOT srcipv4:$exclusions.global.srcipv4

name: CISCO FMC [<%= eventname %>]
description: This rule looks for a high number of Network Intrusion events from same source where action was not blocked.
query: class=cisco_fmc impact=5 NOT action:`blocked` NOT srcipv4:$exclusions.global.srcipv4
